### Require administrator privileges ###
RequireAdmin

### Privacy Tweaks ###
DisableTelemetry
DisableCortana
DisableAppSuggestions
DisableFeedback
DisableErrorReporting
DisableDiagTrack

### Security Tweaks ###
HideDefenderTrayIcon

### Network Tweaks ###
SetCurrentNetworkPrivate
EnableRemoteDesktop
DisableRemoteAssistance

### Service Tweaks ###
EnableUpdateMSProducts
DisableUpdateRestart
DisableAutoplay
DisableAutorun
EnableNTFSLongPaths
EnableClipboardHistory
DisableDefragmentation

### UI Tweaks ###
DisableAccessibilityKeys
ShowTaskManagerDetails
ShowFileOperationsDetails
HideTaskbarSearch
AddENKeyboard

### Explorer UI Tweaks ###
ShowKnownExtensions
SetExplorerThisPC
Hide3DObjectsFromThisPC 

### Application Tweaks ###
DisableIEFirstRun
InstallLinuxSubsystem
InstallHyperV

### Auxiliary Functions ###
WaitForKey
Restart
